postcontent: The Sig Sauer® P238 HD is an exceptionally concealable semi-auto pistol that operates with remarkable reliability. The P238 HD features a stainless steel frame and slide that gives the pistol just enough added weight over polymer-frame pistol designs to enhance controllability during rapid fire considerably, while minimizing felt recoil. Sig P238 pistols are modeled on a 1911-style, single action design, with a thumb safety. The hammer recesses into the beavertail section of the frame to protect it when carrying the weapon on safe, and to avoid hammer-bite while firing. The pistol operates with a locked-breech, short recoil action (instead of blowback) which locks the action closed, resulting in a slide that is easier to rack due to a reduced recoil spring weight. Slide serrations also enhance the shooter's ability to pull the slide back for loading and clearing the action. G-10 grip panels provide a solid hold and enhance durability. The Sig Sauer P238 HD Semi-Auto Pistol comes with SIGLITE® night sights for rapid sight acquisition in any light, including total darkness. title: For Sale:  Look out for the Sig TTT scam
postcontent: This person said "she" posted this pistol in Cincinnati, when you contact to meet "she" tells you she moved to Temple TX and can ship the gun to your FFL.  That is great except "she" wants you to pay in full before she will ship.  She said it takes too much time to change the ad on Armslist to Temple Tx.  I offered to pay to have it shipped to my lcoal gun shop to inspect while it was in the gunshop possession and if it didn't look good, have the gunshop ship it back to her FFl.  That was a no go.  She claims to have lost her husband and is selling his stuff but there is no obituary for him in Cincy where he passed.  She is on Facebook as "Larry".  She confirmed that was her.  She also will not take Paypal.  Cashiers check only.  She said she will only ship after she gets the money.  Seems fishy.  You be the judge.I have asked armslist to take this down.
